    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for your next adventure with this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good, solid condition and has been clearly well-loved and maintained. It offers a smooth, dependable ride and a clean, attractive look that you'll be proud to drive every day. It's a reliable choice that's ready for the road!",
